<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb4046140-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s27"><num value="27">§ 27.</num><heading> Definitions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The terms “State” and “States,” as used in this chapter, shall be held to include the District of Columbia.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb4046141-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1918-07-09/ch143">July 9, 1918, ch. 143</ref>, ch. XV, § 8, <ref href="/us/stat/40/887">40 Stat. 887</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idb4046142-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idb4046143-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idb4046144-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in text, means chapter XV of <ref href="/us/act/1918-07-09/ch143">act July 9, 1918, ch. 143</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/40/887">40 Stat. 887</ref>, which, insofar as classified to the Code, enacted sections 24 to 27 of this title and amended <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s28">section 28 of this title</ref>. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Tables.</p>
</note>
</notes>
